Package chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.diagnostic

Record Class LYnkValidation

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.diagnostic.LYnkValidation
Record Components:
type - Represents the type of return when visiting the parse tree (Use LYnkType)
value - Represents the Object interpretation of a specific input within the code (i.e. could be a statement or an expression
public record LYnkValidation(LYnkType type, Object value) extends Record
Base Object to verify and get back expressions and statements for a LYnk input
